      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions match COU operating envelope; blood analog fluid properties and boundary conditions are documented and traceable.",
      "rationale": "Test conditions are well-documented for four of five operating points. The fifth operating point used a different blood analog batch with slightly different viscosity; batch-to-batch variation is noted but not fully characterized."
    },
    {
