      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metrics (e.g., E%, MAPE) between predicted and measured hemolysis index reported for all operating points with experimental uncertainty bands.",
      "rationale": "Mean absolute percentage error computed for all five operating points. Experimental uncertainty bands are reported for measured hemolysis; however, predicted uncertainty bands are not paired in the comparison plots, reducing the achieved level."
