      "rationale": "The k-omega SST turbulence model and Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model were selected based on literature precedent. No formal model-form sensitivity study comparing alternative turbulence closures or hemolysis models has been conducted. Flagged as epistemic gap."
