      "acceptanceCriteria": "Statistical characterization of experimental sample variability across repeated hemolysis measurements; minimum of three independent replicates per operating point.",
      "rationale": "Experimental data from a single test campaign are available. Replicate measurements were not performed across independent test runs. Sample-to-sample variability in hemolysis measurements is therefore uncharacterized. Flagged as epistemic gap."
